Company Overview of Zall Group Ltd.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Zall Group Ltd., an investment holding company, primarily develops and operates wholesale shopping malls in the People’s Republic of China. The company operates through three segments: Property Development and Related Services; E-commerce and Financial Services; and Supply Chain Management and Trading. Its properties comprise retail units, residential apartments, logistic units, and e-commerce malls. The company also provides financial services, including supply chain finance, guarantees, financial leasing, factoring, and assets management. In addition, it trades in agricultural products; offers leather market management consultation services, property management services, import and export ...
Zall Group Ltd., an investment holding company, primarily develops and operates wholesale shopping malls in the People’s Republic of China. The company operates through three segments: Property Development and Related Services; E-commerce and Financial Services; and Supply Chain Management and Trading. Its properties comprise retail units, residential apartments, logistic units, and e-commerce malls. The company also provides financial services, including supply chain finance, guarantees, financial leasing, factoring, and assets management. In addition, it trades in agricultural products; offers leather market management consultation services, property management services, import and export services, and advertising services, as well as engages in tourism and investment businesses; and provides healthcare products and services. The company was formerly known as Zall Development Group Limited and changed its name to Zall Group Ltd. in June 2016. The company was founded in 1995 and is headquartered in Wuhan, the People’s Republic of China.
