Company Description                    




                        Zall Group Ltd. engages in the development and sale of properties, property management services, development and operation of properties. Zall Group Ltd. is a subsidiary of Zall Development Investment Company Limited. The company was founded in 2010 and is headquartered in Hubei, China.                     


